title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Nov 16 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Nov 16 2021
description:
What better way, Buck asks, than to fight inflation than printing trillions of dollars! A review of the long list of dumb things said by Kenosha nincompoop prosecutors in the Rittenhouse trial. Clay, the lawyer, thinks they may be trying to get a mistrial, but also will be surprised if a not guilty verdict isn't in within 24 hours. This time, Democrats can't blame Trump for any riots. Chinese dissident warns Americans: You’re already in the authoritarian state... you just don’t know it. Governor of Colorado accidentally discovers mask mandates don't work.
